foia:ProcessedRequestSection.foia:FootnoteText: After reviewing their databases, the following components adjusted their number of requests pending as of the start of Fiscal Year 2014: Office of the AG, Office of the DAG, Office of the Assoc. AG, BOP, Civil, Civil Rights, Criminal, DEA, EOIR, NSD, OIP, OIG, OJP, OLP, OLA, Public Affairs, USPC.

FBI included Privacy Act requests for records exempt from the Privacy Act and processed under FOIA in Fiscal Year 2014, which adjusts the number of requests pending as of the start of this Fiscal Year.

During Fiscal Year 2014, EOIR experienced a five week system-wide information technology outage that impeded the ability to process FOIA requests, resulting in an increase in the number of requests pending at the end of this Fiscal Year.
Data contained within this report was impacted due to the government shutdown at the beginning of Fiscal Year 2014.
